{{Expand German|date=September 2010|Über die ästhetische Erziehung des Menschen}}
'''''On the Aesthetic Education of Man''''' (''Über die ästhetische Erziehung des Menschen'') is a treatise by the German author [[Friedrich Schiller]] in the form of a collection of letters. It deals with [[Immanuel Kant]]'s [[Critique of Pure Reason#Transcendental Aesthetic|transcendental aesthetics]] and the events of the [[French Revolution]].

